nodes.text: A moon was located in the Dassal system in the Unknown Regions, orbiting the planetoid Najra-Va, which had been cored out by the First Order. Due to the disappearance of the system's sun, the moon's surface was rocky and cold. A village was located on the moon, but its inhabitants had been massacred. When investigating the system, Poe Dameron and Kazuda Xiono landed on the moon, encountering a spider probe droid.
